                                                                                
                                                                                
Battle Command - written by Richard Gale                                        
                                                                                
in STOS Basic.                          
                                        
                                        
                                        
To play Battle Command either double    
click on BATTLE.PRG from the Desktop,   
or boot STOS and load BATTLE.BAS.       
                                        
                                        
                                        
The Aim of the Game :                   
                                        
         The aim is to simply destroy   
all the incoming missiles and alien     
ships before they destroy the major     
cities on the surrounding planets.      
( a bit like Missile Command really ).  
                                        
Controls :                              
                                        
Use the mouse to direct the gun sight   
and press either mouse key to fire.     
                                        
On each level there are four waves of   
missiles/aliens, as you complete each   
level you will have to shoot more, and  
more aliens or missles.                 
                                        
                                        
                                        
Good Luck.                              
                                        
                                        
